  "excerpt": "Step inside this minimalist New York apartment, featuring a floating stone bed, sleek marble accents, floor-to-ceiling windows, and a monochrome palette that redefines urban simplicity.",
  "siteName": "Home Designing",
  "favicon": "",
  "text": "New York is a city of energy. But in all the chaos, this apartment—designed by Timofei Pivnik—embraces a different philosophy. One of restraint and quiet sophistication. This space is designed with a minimalist approach—where every element serves a purpose. We see the unnecessary being stripped away, creating a home that’s effortlessly elegant. Let’s walk through this apartment and see how minimalism isn’t about emptiness; it’s about intentionality. The living space in this minimalist apartment is an affair of dark gray and white. An expansive white sectional provides plenty of room for lounging, while the large slab of dark marble in the center doubles as a coffee table while adding style. We also see a similar slab within the sofa configuration, giving residents a quick spot to hold their drinks and/or books. The focal point in the living room is the dark gray textured wall on one end and the large potted plants on the other. Large windows are paired with blinds, allowing light to filter in. Next to the living area is the sleek kitchen space. This features a dark gray marble island and four bar stools. The cabinetry is sleek and hardware-less, and appliances are fit right into it. The modern geometric chandelier highlights all the right design features (including the stunning stainless steel sink). The dining area uses a compact table and chair in dark gray. A special mention for the hallway leading to this open-floor plan. It uses dark wooden cabinetry on one end, adding visual interest, and a large mirror on the other, creating a sense of spaciousness. The bedroom in this apartment sticks to a light palette of neutrals. A floating stone platform bed (and integrated nightstand) form an interesting focal point. Sleek rod pendant lights highlight the beauty of the nightstand. A large window allows plenty of natural light to enter. The bedroom also features a compact vanity with a wall-mounted desk and comfy yet stylish ottoman. The bathrooms are a design statement in themselves. We see compact features strategically illuminated by LED lighting. Wall-mounted toilets save space, while the freestanding bathtub makes sure residents can enjoy a luxurious soak within the heart of New York City.",
  "image": "https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gray-island-with-four-barstools.jpg",
  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003carticle id=\"post-208687\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNew York is a city of energy. But in all the chaos, this apartment—\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/timofei_pivnik/\"\u003edesigned by Timofei Pivnik\u003c/a\u003e—embraces a different philosophy. One of restraint and quiet sophistication. This space is designed with a minimalist approach—where every element serves a purpose. We see the unnecessary being stripped away, creating a home that’s effortlessly elegant. Let’s walk through this apartment and see how minimalism isn’t about emptiness; it’s about intentionality.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/living-room-with-textured-wall-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"living room with textured wall\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/living-room-with-textured-wall-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/living-room-with-textured-wall-600x338.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/living-room-with-textured-wall.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" loading=\"lazy\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dark-gray-textured-wall-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"dark gray textured wall\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dark-gray-textured-wall-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dark-gray-textured-wall-600x600.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dark-gray-textured-wall.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" loading=\"lazy\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sectional-sofa-with-marble-slab-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"sectional sofa with marble slab\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sectional-sofa-with-marble-slab-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sectional-sofa-with-marble-slab-600x338.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sectional-sofa-with-marble-slab.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" loading=\"lazy\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-marble-coffee-table-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"sleek marble coffee table\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-marble-coffee-table-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-marble-coffee-table-600x338.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-marble-coffee-table.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-geometric-chandelier-1024x1280.jpg\" alt=\"modern geometric chandelier\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-geometric-chandelier-1024x1280.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-geometric-chandelier-600x750.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-geometric-chandelier.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-marble-kitchen-island-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"black marble kitchen island\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-marble-kitchen-island-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-marble-kitchen-island-600x600.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-marble-kitchen-island.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/minimalistic-gray-kitchen-1024x1280.jpg\" alt=\"minimalistic gray kitchen\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/minimalistic-gray-kitchen-1024x1280.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/minimalistic-gray-kitchen-600x750.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/minimalistic-gray-kitchen.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1250\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gray-island-with-four-barstools.jpg\" alt=\"gray island with four barstools\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gray-island-with-four-barstools.jpg 1000w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gray-island-with-four-barstools-600x750.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/stainless-steel-sink-1024x1280.jpg\" alt=\"stainless steel sink\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/stainless-steel-sink-1024x1280.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/stainless-steel-sink-600x750.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/stainless-steel-sink.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/matte-dark-gray-dining-table-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"matte dark gray dining table\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/matte-dark-gray-dining-table-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/matte-dark-gray-dining-table-600x600.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/matte-dark-gray-dining-table.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hallway-with-dark-wood-cabinetry-1024x1280.jpg\" alt=\"hallway with dark wood cabinetry\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hallway-with-dark-wood-cabinetry-1024x1280.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hallway-with-dark-wood-cabinetry-600x750.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hallway-with-dark-wood-cabinetry.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe living space in this minimalist apartment is an affair of dark gray and white. An expansive white sectional provides plenty of room for lounging, while the large slab of dark marble in the center doubles as a coffee table while adding style. We also see a similar slab within the sofa configuration, giving residents a quick spot to hold their drinks and/or books. The focal point in the living room is the dark gray textured wall on one end and the large potted plants on the other. Large windows are paired with blinds, allowing light to filter in.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eNext to the living area is the sleek kitchen space. This features a dark gray marble island and four bar stools. The cabinetry is sleek and hardware-less, and appliances are fit right into it. The modern geometric chandelier highlights all the right design features (including the stunning stainless steel sink). The dining area uses a compact table and chair in dark gray.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eA special mention for the hallway leading to this open-floor plan. It uses dark wooden cabinetry on one end, adding visual interest, and a large mirror on the other, creating a sense of spaciousness.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/light-and-airy-gray-bedroom-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"light and airy gray bedroom\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/light-and-airy-gray-bedroom-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/light-and-airy-gray-bedroom-600x600.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/light-and-airy-gray-bedroom.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/floating-stone-platform-bed-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"floating stone platform bed\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/floating-stone-platform-bed-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/floating-stone-platform-bed-600x600.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/floating-stone-platform-bed.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-rod-pendant-lights-over-stone-nightstand-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"sleek rod pendant lights over stone nightstand\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-rod-pendant-lights-over-stone-nightstand-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-rod-pendant-lights-over-stone-nightstand-600x600.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-rod-pendant-lights-over-stone-nightstand.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/large-windows-with-blinds-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"large windows with blinds\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/large-windows-with-blinds-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/large-windows-with-blinds-600x600.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/large-windows-with-blinds.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1250\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compact-vanity-in-light-gray-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"compact vanity in light gray bedroom\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compact-vanity-in-light-gray-bedroom.jpg 1000w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compact-vanity-in-light-gray-bedroom-600x750.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-gray-vanity-1024x1280.jpg\" alt=\"sleek gray vanity\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-gray-vanity-1024x1280.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-gray-vanity-600x750.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-gray-vanity.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe bedroom in this apartment sticks to a light palette of neutrals. A floating stone platform bed (and integrated nightstand) form an interesting focal point. Sleek rod pendant lights highlight the beauty of the nightstand. A large window allows plenty of natural light to enter. The bedroom also features a compact vanity with a wall-mounted desk and comfy yet stylish ottoman.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-sink-and-led-illuminated-mirror-1024x1280.jpg\" alt=\"sleek sink and led illuminated mirror\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-sink-and-led-illuminated-mirror-1024x1280.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-sink-and-led-illuminated-mirror-600x750.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sleek-sink-and-led-illuminated-mirror.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dark-gray-bathroom-interior-with-strategic-lighting-1024x1280.jpg\" alt=\"dark gray bathroom interior with strategic lighting\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dark-gray-bathroom-interior-with-strategic-lighting-1024x1280.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dark-gray-bathroom-interior-with-strategic-lighting-600x750.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dark-gray-bathroom-interior-with-strategic-lighting.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/wall-mounted-toilet-in-gray-bathroom-1024x1280.jpg\" alt=\"wall mounted toilet in gray bathroom\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/wall-mounted-toilet-in-gray-bathroom-1024x1280.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/wall-mounted-toilet-in-gray-bathroom-600x750.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/wall-mounted-toilet-in-gray-bathroom.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-hardware-in-shower-cubicle-1024x1280.jpg\" alt=\"black hardware in shower cubicle\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-hardware-in-shower-cubicle-1024x1280.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-hardware-in-shower-cubicle-600x750.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-hardware-in-shower-cubicle.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/led-illuminated-bathroom-vanity-1024x1280.jpg\" alt=\"led illuminated bathroom vanity\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/led-illuminated-bathroom-vanity-1024x1280.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/led-illuminated-bathroom-vanity-600x750.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/led-illuminated-bathroom-vanity.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/freestanding-bathtub-1024x1280.jpg\" alt=\"freestanding bathtub\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/freestanding-bathtub-1024x1280.jpg 1024w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/freestanding-bathtub-600x750.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/freestanding-bathtub.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe bathrooms are a design statement in themselves. We see compact features strategically illuminated by LED lighting. Wall-mounted toilets save space, while the freestanding bathtub makes sure residents can enjoy a luxurious soak within the heart of New York City.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
